relevant_communication:
We started its activities with the initiative group in the field of HIV and STIs among MSM in 2001. The organization itself was incorporated in 2002. During this time, we have become the largest MSM-service NGOs in Ukraine, efficiently implemented more than 20 projects and studies among MSM. It is allowed to reach 40% coverage of MSM audience receiving services in the field of HIV and STI prevention in Ukraine.  
Main services organizations today are:  
- Outreach / social work;  
- Testing for HIV and STIs, counseling "peer to peer";  
- Work of community center for MSM / LGBT people;  
- Social mobilization and budget advocacy at the interests of key groups IDUs, sex workers, MSM, former prisoners at the local levels;  
- Support of HIV positive MSM;  
- Rapid testing of MSM for hepatitis B and C and linkage to care.
